import React from "react"
import ContentLoader from "react-content-loader"

const Loader = (props) => (
  <ContentLoader
    speed={2}
    width={310}
    height={310}
    viewBox="0 0 310 310"
    backgroundColor="#d6d6d6"
    foregroundColor="#ecebeb"
    props
  >
    <rect x="12" y="352" rx="7" ry="7" width="260" height="29" />
    <rect x="21" y="21" rx="0" ry="0" width="197" height="190" />
    <rect x="22" y="219" rx="0" ry="0" width="197" height="21" />
  </ContentLoader>
)

export default Loader
